.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different games are played: go, backgammon, mah-jongg, whist
4 different pets are kept: hamster, goldfish, horse, turtle
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the hamster is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing whist is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8
5. the person playing go is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the person playing go is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Game   | mah-jongg   | backgammon         | whist   | go    |
| Pet         | goldfish | turtle | horse | hamster |

