.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, pop, electronic, funk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, poppy, aconite, begonia
1. the fan of funk is somewhere between the fan of punk and the fan of pop##7
2. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the person who growsaconite##5
3. the fan of funk is somewhere between the fan of electronic and the fan of punk##7
4. the fan of electronic is not to the left of the person who growsbegonia##8
5. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere between the fan of pop and the person who growspoppy##7
6. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the fan of funk##5
7. the person who growspoppy is not to the left of the fan of punk##8
8. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | electronic | funk | punk    |
| Flower         | marigold | begonia   | aconite   | poppy |

