.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up, sprite, mirinda
House: futuristic, palace, farmhouse, townhouse
1. the townhouse house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
2. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
4. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
5. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
6. the person drinking mirinda is not to the left of the palace house##8
7. the person drinking mirinda is the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage          | mirinda | tea | 7up  | sprite |
| House   | palace   | townhouse         | farmhouse | futuristic |

