.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
House: gothic-revival, craftsman, futuristic, colonial
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, baccarat, davidoff, dannemann
1. the baccarat-smoker is not to the left of the craftsman house##8
2. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere between the colonial house and the davidoff-smoker##7
3. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the old-henry-smoker##5
4. the dannemann-smoker is not to the left of the old-henry-smoker##8
5. the dannemann-smoker is not to the left of the craftsman house##8
6. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
7. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
8. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| House   | craftsman      | futuristic | gothic-revival | colonial   |
| Cigar      | old-henry | davidoff | dannemann  | baccarat |

