3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person drinking mirinda##7
5. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
6. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person drinking iced-tea##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Beverage     | mirinda | iced-tea | cola | tea     |
| Hobby   | reading   | baking        | video-games          | photography |

