3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who growszinniapy##3
4. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who growssunflower is not the person who's hobby is gardening##6
7. the person who growszinnia is not to the right of the person who growssunflower##8
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Flower   | zinnia   | zinniapy | sunflower | rose |
| Hobby     | dancing | collecting       | rock-climbing  | gardening    |

