3. the person playing chess is on the left of the game-smoker##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the havana-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person playing billiard and the game-smoker##7
7. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
8. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar   | havana | game         | blend    | davidoff       |
| Game      | chess | backgammon | canasta | billiard |

