4. the person playing bridge is between the person playing scrabble and the owner of the ferret##2
5. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
