.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
City: venice, edinburgh, boston, marseilles
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, blood-red, blue, lavender
 1. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5
 2. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the person traveling to boston##8
 3. the person traveling to venice is the person who likes blue##1
 4. the person who likes blue is not to the right of the person who likes blood-red##8
 5. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 6. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to boston##5
 7. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person traveling to venice is not to the right of the person who likes blue##8
 9. the person who likes blood-red is not to the left of the person traveling to venice##8
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is not to the left of the person who likes coral##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| City          | edinburgh    | boston | venice | marseilles |
| Color   | coral | lavender  | blue     | blood-red    |

